General.Name: Corem Property Group AB Pfd.
General.Description: Corem Property Group AB (publ), a real estate company, owns, manages, and develops industrial, warehouse, logistics, and retail properties in the Nordic region. As of December 31, 2021, it had 518 properties with a total lettable area of 3,479 thousand square kilometers. Corem Property Group AB (publ) was incorporated in 1993 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
